page.title: 12HOME LIFE IN WOODLAND P.M.
page.content: After{dinner}Rebecca and I went for a bike ride to Romaldkirk which is 7 miles away and it was hard because there were lots of big hills. We had our{tea}at Rebecca's Nana's. We had sandwiches,cakes,biscuits and drinks.After our tea we{set off home again.It was even harder going back because it was nearly all uphill.It was about 7.00p.m.when we got home. I went to{bed}at about 9.30p.m. and watched 'Thats Life' on T.V.My bedroom has pink and white wallpaper, bedspread,curtains and lampshade and a pink carpet. Before I closed the curtains I looked out of my bedroom window and looked at the view.
